{"tid":1366260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【跪求入嚟睇睇】你話我係「和理非」我都係咁講～","createTime":"2019-07-26T01:55:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T07:46:36.000Z","uid":149806,"like":17,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6cd16cbca73d003a510fc5e5e10d178d224c6467","tid":1366260,"uid":149806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:55:37.000Z","msg":"請大家幫忙轉發~<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W9y4vUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW9y4vUF.jpg&h=9aa48b35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>「7．27，不破壞，不起扛，不指罵、不暴力」</strong><br />\n<br />\n元朗，是你和我一起成長的家。由出生、讀書、結婚、成家立室，很多元朗人在這裏生活了幾十年。<br />\n<br />\n即使你不住元朗，B仔、燒賣皇后、豬油撈飯、永年、大榮華馬拉糕，都是你和我的共同回憶。<br />\n<br />\n可惜，這個星期，我們熟悉的元朗變得不一樣。<br />\n<br />\n早上上班，我們要停一停，想一想該穿甚麼顏色的上衣；<br />\n為了令家人放心，入黑前要趕回家；<br />\n宵夜店原本遍布市中心，打風落雨年中無休，星期一晚，一切都沒有；<br />\n還有&hellip;還有&hellip;我們還要擔心，有沒有下一次&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n元朗人，這個星期都流過淚、徹夜難眠。星期六，大家又再為元朗擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n不論你堅持參與遊行、或反對遊行；不論你想政府回應多少個訴求；不論你有多想追究星期日晚的事；不論你有多想林鄭下台，或者支持林鄭；不論你對警察有甚麼意見；不論你是左中右&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n用籐條教仔，不會令爭取民主的聲音消失；<br />\n但拆祠堂，不會得到民主，只會破壞圍村的文化和傳統。<br />\n<br />\n以武力擊退示威者，不會令人民的聲音壓下去；<br />\n但堵路、斷水斷電，對惡勢力沒有絲毫影響，卻懲罰了無辜的市民、村民。<br />\n<br />\n以暴易暴，升級容易，放下才是最難。我們希望所有元朗人，所有會來元朗的人，都同樣愛護這個地方，愛護這裏每一個人。只有懂得愛、懂得珍惜、懂得放下仇恨，我們才能真正對抗暴力，重見我們熟悉的元朗、熟悉的香港。<br />\n<br />\n過了這個星期六，元朗的你和我，都應該要有機會無憂的安睡，而不再是擔驚受怕，不再為各種廝殺而流淚。<br />\n<br />\n不要暴力，放下仇恨，免卻恐懼！<br />\n<br />\n一群愛元朗的人   上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ksprKey.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FksprKey.jpg&h=d0d0c897&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J5mBm1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ5mBm1d.jpg&h=ad4dff56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZdgUS7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZdgUS7U.jpg&h=3e5e8c05&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VVuCQUz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVVuCQUz.jpg&h=83d83142&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f3c095b2879e66b8cefbea87b542a15b86b4ba7","tid":1366260,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:57:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8cdef3adc47d4fde0465620a0286df7dba7865","tid":1366260,"uid":266060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:57:42.000Z","msg":"和理<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>優</strong></span>"},{"pid":"b8acdf21b9bd9c748a2247ef828df679605f1786","tid":1366260,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21b3657debaeb952e2536eaa67c3a95a78b63a0","tid":1366260,"uid":265019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:59:59.000Z","msg":"同意 唔可以比政權覺得係政見不同者的紛爭！"},{"pid":"2a41ed6cc93dfeaa0eedbd06da3a61cd46e3153a","tid":1366260,"uid":265019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:00:49.000Z","msg":"對準政權 係反警黑勾結 不是針對私怨！"},{"pid":"5fe63b9d38b3ca2bce4d747cb6978b7475616f0b","tid":1366260,"uid":265019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:01:25.000Z","msg":"而家個個傳我地會暴力報復 我地就和理非比佢睇"},{"pid":"ca57fd9b7d6e2b48402ff04a29cb64414252c09c","tid":1366260,"uid":265019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:01:51.000Z","msg":"我一向欣賞勇武 但今次非和理非不可！"},{"pid":"8a53b86d5622353d601a62a09650d0e588b2c0ea","tid":1366260,"uid":54181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:02:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6709dabd705767d3a0a13c6ed4a5804d2e8a5cd","tid":1366260,"uid":149806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a53b86d5622353d601a62a09650d0e588b2c